{"tid":2267602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（拜登領先）民意調查顯示 trump於全國落後8個百分點！！！","createTime":"2020-11-02T07:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T08:00:13.000Z","uid":111153,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dd91f5d52395e2c71507d0ab6929b992a75ccf47","tid":2267602,"uid":111153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:49:45.000Z","msg":"RTHK<br />\n拜登支持率領先　特朗普質疑大選日之後仍受理郵遞選票<br />\n<br />\n美國大選在當地星期二舉行，爭取連任的總統特朗普據報向助手表示，如果大選日當晚點票結果顯示他的得票率領先，他就會宣布自己勝選。不過，特朗普否認有關報道，但他質疑，在大選日之後仍受理郵遞選票是否公平。特朗普和民主黨總統候選人繼續盡最後努力拉票。民意調查顯示，拜登在全國的支持度以大約8個百分點的優勢領先。超過9300萬名選民已透過郵遞或親身去票站提早投票，佔上屆大選投票人數六成七。另外，拜登陣營一輛宣傳巴士，日前在得州被特朗普支持者車輛包圍，拜登陣營報警求助，警方其後到場，並護送宣傳巴士駛往原定目的地，聯邦調查局正調查事件。<br />\n<br />\n2020-11-02 15:40:14"},{"pid":"4a56bd1a76e0097dc0fb6b45bf69c1a43f22af4e","tid":2267602,"uid":111153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:50:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79c2f6db47337e50dcd55397944b8b676f478b40","tid":2267602,"uid":123264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:50:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />報警撚"},{"pid":"aae591d195d77fa54b5d4b90a8c961d93e4714a0","tid":2267602,"uid":174767,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:51:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scubadiverlife.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/04/AdobeStock_24621260-1024x683.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscubadiverlife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F04%2FAdobeStock_24621260-1024x683.jpeg&h=79e70146&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d521a1423a47643961862f2632c5a14b9a52df1c","tid":2267602,"uid":155095,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T07:51:53.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\">連燈仔係時候面對現實<br />\n<br />\n快啲轉軚向習大大效忠</span>"},{"